data.description: Don't let this lil country peace of paradise deceive you ! This gorgeous lil home is more spacious than it looks ..you have to come see it to believe it ! This is a custom built home 2016 , so all the systems are still new and working great ! It is a perfect home for anyone who wants to have a farm life . The primary bedroom has 2 huge walk-in closets and a luscious whirlpool Jacuzzi inline heated tub for those nights after working hard , the second bedroom has a safe room built in the closet , the third bedroom has its own bathroom as well .. and there is gorgeous kitchen with an island for some good home cooking , a mother in law suite is a part of this home including a kitchen , living room and bathroom and outside entrance , the back patio to the main home has a hot tub and an above ground pool for the family to enjoy , the land is fully fenced with a Pipe and barb wire fencing - corral w/ working pins to work your horses and cattle , grain bins for storage , 30X45 barn w/ electricity , 20X24 shed w/ electricity with water accessibility close by , red iron barn /horse barn 30X40 w/ electricity w/water accessibility near by , 2 ponds , plenty of open pasture to run at least 30 -40 head of cattle , beautiful trees and wildlife , 4 miles from the Arkansas River and about 8 from the Illinois river , some of the best sand bass fishin' around ,another added bonus is Solar panels come with this home and greatly reduce your electric bill!!
